## 🌐 Pages

| Page | File | Description |
|---|---|---|
| Homepage | `index.html` | Hero, services, proof, process, portfolio, testimonials |
| About | `pages/about.html` | Story, values, team, approach |
| Services | `pages/services.html` | Full service details + pricing |
| Contact | `pages/contact.html` | Channel cards, form, trust section |

---

## ⚙️ JavaScript Modules (`main.js`)

| Function | Description |
|---|---|
| `initLenis()` | Smooth scroll via Lenis |
| `initFloatingHeader()` | Header appears after 80px scroll |
| `initMobileNav()` | Hamburger drawer open/close |
| `initBackToTop()` | FAB button appears after 400px scroll |
| `initScrollReveal()` | Entrance animations on scroll |
| `initCounters()` | Animated number counters |
| `initScrollSpy()` | Active nav link on scroll |
| `initSmoothAnchors()` | Anchor links use Lenis |
| `initFooterYear()` | Dynamic copyright year |
| `initCursorGlow()` | Gold glow follows cursor (desktop only) |
| `initCardTilt()` | 3D tilt on cards (desktop hover) |
| `initTestimonialCarousel()` | Auto-play slider with swipe support |

---

## 🖼️ Replacing Image Placeholders

All placeholder `<div>` slots include a comment with the exact `<img>` tag to use.

Search for `image-placeholder` in any HTML file to find all slots.

Example replacement:
```html
<!-- Before -->
<div class="image-placeholder port-img-ph" role="img" aria-label="...">
  ...
</div>

<!-- After -->
<img src="../assets/imgs/project-aurora.jpg"
     alt="Aurora Fashion Store homepage"
     width="1200" height="700"
     loading="lazy" />
```

Recommended formats: **WebP** (best) or JPG. SVG for logos.

---

## 📱 Responsive Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Target |
|---|---|
| No query (base) | Mobile — 320px+ |
| `max-width: 1024px` | Tablet |
| `max-width: 900px` | Navigation collapse |
| `max-width: 640px` | Mobile overrides |
| `max-width: 380px` | Very small screens |

---

## 🔗 Internal Link Reference

When linking between pages, use these paths:

**From `index.html` (root):**
```html
<a href="pages/about.html">About</a>
<a href="pages/services.html">Services</a>
<a href="pages/contact.html">Contact</a>
```

**From `pages/*.html`:**
```html
<a href="../index.html">Home</a>
<a href="about.html">About</a>
<a href="services.html">Services</a>
<a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
```

