## ✅ Deployment Checklist

Before going live:

- [ ] Replace all image placeholders with real images
- [ ] Update `hello@okwebstart.com` with real email
- [ ] Update `+44 (0) 1234 567 890` with real phone
- [ ] Update all social media links
- [ ] Replace `https://www.okwebstart.com` with real domain in all canonical/OG tags
- [ ] Add real `favicon.ico`, `favicon.svg`, `apple-touch-icon.png`
- [ ] Create `site.webmanifest` for PWA support
- [ ] Create `og-image.jpg` (1200×630px) for social sharing
- [ ] Test on Chrome, Safari, Firefox and mobile devices
- [ ] Run Lighthouse audit (target: 90+ on all categories)

